### Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000/health

### Create Email Task (Immediate)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Send Welcome Email",
  "taskType": "email",
  "payload": "{\"to\":\"user@example.com\",\"subject\":\"Welcome!\",\"body\":\"Hello World\"}",
  "priority": 5,
  "maxRetries": 3
}

### Create Report Task (High Priority)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Generate Monthly Report",
  "taskType": "report",
  "payload": "{\"reportType\":\"monthly-sales\"}",
  "priority": 9,
  "maxRetries": 3
}

### Create Scheduled Task (5 minutes from now)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Scheduled Email",
  "taskType": "email",
  "payload": "{\"to\":\"admin@example.com\",\"subject\":\"Reminder\",\"body\":\"This is scheduled\"}",
  "scheduledTime": "{{$datetime iso8601 300}}",
  "priority": 5
}

### Get All Tasks
GET http://localhost:5000/api/tasks?page=1&pageSize=20

### Get Task by ID (replace with actual ID)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/tasks/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### Get Tasks by Status
GET http://localhost:5000/api/tasks?status=Completed&page=1&pageSize=10

### Get Metrics
GET http://localhost:5000/api/metrics

### Create Recurring Task (Every minute)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/recurring-tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Hourly Health Check",
  "taskType": "email",
  "payload": "{\"to\":\"ops@example.com\",\"subject\":\"Health Check\",\"body\":\"System OK\"}",
  "cronExpression": "* * * * *",
  "priority": 3,
  "maxRetries": 2
}

### Get All Recurring Tasks
GET http://localhost:5000/api/recurring-tasks

### Disable Recurring Task (replace with actual ID)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/recurring-tasks/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/disable

### Enable Recurring Task (replace with actual ID)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/recurring-tasks/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/enable
